html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        title Mithril Web Design
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/bootstrap.css")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="static/css/style.css")

    body(class='align-items-center') 


        section(class='row p-5 text-center')
            div(class='col')
                h1 What Tech I Use

        section(class='row text-center hover-effect text-light')
            div(class='col-sm p-5 border')
                i(class='fa-brands fa-node-js fa-2xl pb-2')
                h2 NodeJs
                p NodeJs allows me to make websites dynamic and do a lot of work on the backend to make sure your website is fast!
            div(class='col-sm p-5 border')
                i(class="fa-brands fa-js fa-2xl pb-2")
                h2 Javascript
                p Javascript is a fundamental building block of websites. Whether you like it or not, it's here to stay.
            div(class='col-sm p-5 border')
                i(class='fa-solid fa-truck-fast fa-2xl pb-2')
                h2 Express
                p Express allows me to do quick routing, so things on your site can be found
        

        section(class='row text-center align-items-center')
            div(class='col-sm-1')
                h2 About Me
                p I am a father first and foremost. I have 2 beautiful children that encouraged me to start doing this for a living. My daughter actually helps me design wireframes. I love code, solving problems, and creating things from scratch. Overall I'm a giant nerd and I love it!
            div(class='col-sm-1')
                img(class="img-fluid" src="static/images/computer.gif" alt="computer animation")

        
        
        
        section(class='row p-5 text-center bg-dark text-light align-items-center')
            div(class='col-sm-1')
                img(class='img' src="static/images/logo-transparent-svg.svg", alt="mithril logo")
            div(class='col-sm-1')
                h2 My process
                p The process includes a lot of communication. From beginning to end, I explain and help you understand every move that I make. I can put together a website with everything that you need! let me know what your idea is and we'll talk!
        
        
